{"tid":2405013,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"[震驚] 澳洲總理表示並不會為港人提供新永居簽證類別","createTime":"2021-02-12T05:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T12:02:10.000Z","uid":156394,"like":8,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6ffa8070ee59731ddb018203d9af850c049e27cd","tid":2405013,"uid":156394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:25:31.000Z","msg":"總理莫理遜（Scott Morrison）表示，獲延長簽證5年的港人臨時技術簽證或畢業生簽證持有人，在5年期屆滿後，可申請「技術類別」的永久居留簽證，但須具備「適當技能」。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">[member]簡單d講\n如果5年內你申請唔到189(洲政府擔保)/190(獨立技術移民)\n你係唔會有機會再留得番係澳洲\n除咗香港人畢業後個簽證可以留長d係澳洲外\n係同其他國家想移民嘅朋友係無分別\n一樣係個堆簽證入面競爭[/member]</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/chinese/cantonese/zh-hant/audio/hong-kongers-need-to-have-the-appropriate-skills-for-a-skilled-visa-after-5-year-temporary-visa-period-says-morrison?fbclid=IwAR31W3a53Z2NMM8O5wrefLCQkm06LCO0hcXCgoV9lIs9ifniNxGje_I7sbI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Fchinese%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Faudio%2Fhong-kongers-need-to-have-the-appropriate-skills-for-a-skilled-visa-after-5-year-temporary-visa-period-says-morrison%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR31W3a53Z2NMM8O5wrefLCQkm06LCO0hcXCgoV9lIs9ifniNxGje_I7sbI&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FNVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=ae3bf6bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/chinese/cantonese/zh-hant/audio/hong-kongers-need-to-have-the-appropriate-skills-for-a-skilled-visa-after-5-year-temporary-visa-period-says-morrison?fbclid=IwAR31W3a53Z2NMM8O5wrefLCQkm06LCO0hcXCgoV9lIs9ifniNxGje_I7sbI</a>"},{"pid":"a3c3b269ffb96f5c185dbce694e0c71130e8e638","tid":2405013,"uid":130079,"like":13,"dislike":20,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:26:38.000Z","msg":"過去係make Australia great again<br />\n唔係要人地簽證就哂香港人"},{"pid":"c5a9dc2a1c34f5fcda8fa61a846661a54f26c610","tid":2405013,"uid":8410,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:26:40.000Z","msg":"跟美國縮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkg